.TH LIGHTNING-NODE-LISTFORWARDS-IN-MST-VARIANCE 1
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listforwards-in-msat-variance \- variance of inbound forwarded amounts
.SH SYNOPSIS
lightning node-listforwards-in-msat-variance
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the variance of inbound millisatoshi amounts across forwarded payments.
.SH OUTPUT
JSON object with key in_msat_variance.
